        {
            "id": 6311565,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 典範(3372)大漲7.26%，報23.65元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>典範(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3372:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3372\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3372-TW</a>)15日12:59股價上漲1.6元，報23.65元，漲幅7.26%，成交2,496張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>典範(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3372:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3372\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3372-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為IC封裝及測試。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌2.65%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.25%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-426 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-336 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-90 張</li> <li>融資增減：-38 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
